AzureBlobLease

Simple Windows tool to manage Azure storage blobs and leases.

- Works with page and block blobs.
- Create and release leases on blobs.
- create/delete Azure storage container policies
- Retrieve container Shared Access Signature (SAS)

Update history
--------------
5/21/13
Improved storage account handling

5/20/13
Added support for creating/deleting container policies, and getting container SAS.

2/26/14
Minor refactoring




